    "notes": "Effective @subjects per experiment after inheritance: Experiment 1 → paper-level (n=4); Experiment 2a → its own (n=6); Experiment 2b → paper-level (n=4). Inheritance is a post-parse semantic operation; the AST stores the declarations as written."
